# PhotoMapApp

Photo Map Explorer - View your photos on a map with object detection.

## Features

- 📷 Load photos from any folder
- 🗺️ Display photo locations on an interactive map
- 🔍 Search photos by filename, detected objects, or coordinates
- ✨ Analyze photos to detect objects using Vision framework
- 📊 See detection results with confidence percentages

## Requirements

- macOS 13.0+
- Xcode 15.0+

## Building

1. Clone the repository
2. Open `PhotoMapApp.xcodeproj` in Xcode
3. Press ⌘B to build
4. Press ⌘R to run

## How to Use

1. Click "Select Folder" to choose a folder with photos
2. Click "Analyze All" to detect objects in all photos
3. Use the search bar to find photos by filename, detected objects, or coordinates
